          "highlight": [
            "Ms."
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "請在今日下班前將合約寄給陳女士。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "Two Mses from the marketing department presented the new strategy.",
          "highlight": [
            "Mses"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "行銷部門的兩位女士提出了新的策略。"
          }
